<TEXT>
garlic lovers will savor garlic bread 
garlic soup garlic squid garlic veggies and even garlic cake and 
ice cream at a california towns annual festival celebrating the 
pungent herb 
ive been going for 12 years and i still havent got close to 
sampling everything you can eat in one weekend said j chris 
dowell who is helping to organize the threeday gilroy garlic 
festival which opened friday gilroy is situated 30 miles south of 
san jose 
the food festival was started in 1979 to boost the towns claim 
to be the garlic capital of the world even though the fresno area 
produces most of the states garlic 
more than 140000 people attended last year devouring 77760 
servings of garlic bread 35135 helpings of pasta con pesto and 
24835 pepper steak sandwiches nearly 30000 gallons of beer and 
28000 glasses of wine washed down the aromatic meals 
the attendance is expected to rise this year to around 150000 
organizers said 
food booths make use of more than a ton of minced fresh garlic 
the festival features a recipe contest cooking demonstrations by 
noted chefs and displays of garlicinspired art 
