collar wife and mother with three kids denied she was 
disrespectful 
i represent a certain part of america that probably nobody 
else represents she said and i came out of someplace and got 
someplace and ive got a right to sing the song 
she recalled how in the first few notes of the starspangled 
banner she knew things were going wrong 
then everybody started booing me and i went into this panic 
thing she said at a raucous news conference friday at the 
beverly hilton hotel it took all the guts ive got in my life to 
finish singing 
more than 2000 phone calls about the unmelodious performance 
had come into the padres switchboard by midday friday 
barr said she had the best of intentions she refused to 
apologize although she used the word sorry several times 
im not going to apologize for doing it she said but not 
anybody anticipated that it would be this negative 
she capped her solo by grabbing her crotch and spitting 
actions she described as a parody of a baseball player not a 
response to the boos 
i probably should have waited a while before i scratched 
myself and spit she said but i wanted to get out of there 
the news conference became as chaotic as her tv family on 
roseanne when her husband tom arnold ordered police to eject 
a tabloid photographer 
