radio station declared the dissolution of does government and 
promised to hold elections in six months taylor said the doe 
government was to be replaced by a national patriotic 
reconstruction assembly of which he will be leader 
but reports from rebelheld territory said taylor remained 30 
miles from the front and his forces were making little progress 
